sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant P as Player<br/>(mobile)
    participant W as WebClient<br/>oyna.pro
    participant O as Operator<br/>(admin)
    participant B as Backend<br/>CRM
    participant M as Middleware<br/>(Room Agent)
    participant U as UE<br/>(Game Client)

    Note over O,U: Сценарий: 2 игрока, Classic режим, 10-минутная сессия

    %% 1. Topup
    O->>B: POST /admin/users/{id}/topup {minutes: 20, price: 2000}
    B->>B: user.balanceMinutes += 20
    B-->>O: 201 {transactionId, balanceAfter: 20}

    %% 2. Create session
    O->>B: POST /sessions {stationId, mode: "classic"}
    B->>B: Create session (status=CREATED)
    B-->>O: 201 {sessionId, joinCode, qrImageUrl}
    B--)M: WS push: session_created
    M--)U: session_created
    U->>U: Show QR on screen
    U--)M: qr_shown
    M->>B: POST /sessions/{id}/confirm-qr-shown
    B->>B: status → WAITING

    %% 3. Players scan QR
    P->>W: Open /join/{joinCode}
    W->>W: Login user
    W->>B: POST /users/me/join-session {joinCode}
    B->>B: Check balance >= 10
    B->>B: transaction (deduction, 10 min)
    B->>B: Create MatchPlayer (slot=0)
    B-->>W: 200 {slot: 0, balanceAfter: 10}
    B--)M: WS push: player_joined (slot=0)
    M--)U: player_joined
    U->>U: Show "Aybar" at slot 0

    Note over P,U: (Второй игрок то же самое, slot=1)

    %% 4. Operator starts
    O->>B: POST /sessions/{id}/start
    B->>B: status → STARTING
    B-->>O: 200 {status: STARTING, players: [...]}
    B--)M: WS push: session_start
    M--)U: session_start {countdownSeconds: 3, players: [...]}
    U->>U: Show 3-2-1 Countdown
    U--)M: countdown_started
    M->>B: (not critical, just log)

    %% 5. Playing
    Note over U: Game loop: level 1
    U->>U: Start level 1 (90 sec timer)
    U--)M: match_started {level: 1, attemptNumber: 1}
    M->>B: POST /sessions/{id}/matches (201 created)

    Note over U: Players pass level 1 in 42 sec
    U->>U: OnLevelComplete {score: 1920, livesLeft: 3}
    U--)M: match_completed {level: 1, score: 1920, bVictory: true}
    M->>B: POST /sessions/{id}/matches (Idempotency-Key: sess-L1-A1)
    B-->>M: 201 {matchId, created: true}

    Note over U: 5-sec break, then level 2
    U->>U: Start level 2
    U--)M: match_started {level: 2}
    M->>B: POST /matches

    Note over U: Players pass level 2, total time 7.5 min
    U->>U: OnLevelComplete
    U--)M: match_completed {level: 2, score: 1500, bVictory: true}
    M->>B: POST /matches

    Note over U: Level 3 starts but session timer kills it
    U->>U: Start level 3 (1 min remaining in session)
    U--)M: match_started {level: 3}
    M->>B: POST /matches

    Note over U: Session timer reaches 0
    U->>U: Session timeout, level 3 marked as failed
    U--)M: match_completed {level: 3, score: 0, bVictory: false, failReason: "session_ended"}
    M->>B: POST /matches

    %% 6. Session end
    U--)M: session_ended {reason: "time_elapsed", matchesPlayed: 3, totalScore: 3420}
    M->>B: POST /sessions/{id}/end (Idempotency-Key: sess-end)
    B->>B: Calculate rating for each player
    B->>B: Update user_rating (all_time, monthly, daily)
    B->>B: Insert rating_events (for per-venue aggregation)
    B->>B: status → COMPLETED
    B-->>M: 200 {ratingDelta: {user1: +280, user2: +280}}
    M--)U: (optional) session_summary with rating delta
    U->>U: Show Session Summary screen (5 sec)
    U->>U: Return to idle, ready for next session
